[{"Id": 1016640, "EnglishTitle": "PLEASE NOTE: Be it clear that the reason for presenting Translation is to understand Salaat and to recite in Arabic with concentration because reciting Salaat other than Arabic language (or Transliteration) is not correct.", "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": "Waazeh rahe keh tarjuma-e-namaz pesh karne ki asal wajah namaz samajh ke Arabi mein khuzoo aur tawajjoh ke saath namaz padhna hai. Kyu’n keh Arabi ya Roman-Arabi (Transliteration) ke siwa kisi aur zabaan mein namaz padhna sahih nahin hai.", "UrduTitle": "واضح رہے کہ ترجمۂ نماز پیش کرنے کی اصل غرض نماز سمجھ کے عربی میں خضوع اور توجہ کے ساتھ نماز پڑھنا ہے۔ کیوں کہ عربی کے سوا کسی اور زبان میں نماز پڑھنا صحیح نہیں ہے۔ اس لئے ہر ایک کے لئے نماز کی حد تک قرآن و عربی سیکھنا واجب ہے۔", "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1002811, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "The Infallible Imams (a) are reported to have said that a servant (of Allah) may offer 8 rakat namaz on Friday, in the form of 2 rakats each. 4 rakats of these may be dedicated to the Holy Prophet (s) while the other 4 rakats to Lady Fatema (s). On Saturday, other 4 rakats namaz are offered and dedicated to Imam Ali (a). Likewise, 4 rakats namaz may be offered every day and dedicated to one of the Holy Imams respectively. Thus, on Thursday, 4 rakats are offered and dedicated to Imam Sadiq (a). On Friday, 8 rakats are offered; 4 rakats of them are dedicated to the Holy Prophet (s) and 4 rakats to Lady Fatema (s). On Saturday, 4 rakats namaz are offered and dedicated to Imam Kazim (a). Likewise, 4 rakats namaz may be offered every day and dedicated to one of the Holy Imams respectively. Hence, on Thursday, the 4 rakats namaz are dedicated to Imam Mahdi (atfs). Each day after every 2 rakats recite the following…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Masoomeen (a) se riwaayat ki gayi hai keh insaan ko Juma (Friday) ke din 8 rakat namaz adaa kare (2x2) rakat kar ke padhe jis mein pehli 4 rakate’n Rasoole Khuda (s) ko hadiya kare aur dusri 4 rakate’n Janabe Zahra (s) ko hadiya kare. Isi tarah Saturday ke roz 4 rakat namaz padh kar Hazrat Imam Ali (a) ko hadiya kare, neez har roz 4 rakat namaz padhe aur tarteeb ke saath ek ek Imam (a) ko hadiya karta rahe yahan tak keh Thursday ke din 4 rakat padh kar Imam Jafar Sadiq (a) ke liye hadiya kare. Phir roze Juma (Friday) 8 rakat namaz adaa kare aur pehle ki tarah 4 rakat Rasoole Khuda (s) aur 4 rakat Janabe Zahra (s) ko hadiya kare phir Saturday ke din 4 rakat namaz padh kar Imam Moosa Kazim (a) ko hadiya kare aur is tarah rozaana 4 rakat namaz padh kar tarteeb ke saath har Imam ko hadiya karta jaaye. Chunaan-che Thursday ke din 4 rakat namaz adaa kar ke Hazrat Imam’e Asr (a) ke liye hadiya kare aur rozana har 2 rakat ke baad is dua ko padhe…", "UrduDescription": "معصومینؑ سے روایت کی گئی ہے کہ انسان کو جمعہ کے دن آٹھ رکعت نماز ادا کرنی چاہیے کہ جس میں ہر دوسری رکعت میں سلام پڑھے پہلی چار رکعتیں رسول خدا ؐکو ہدیہ کرے اور دوسری چار رکعتیں جناب زہرا ؑکو ہدیہ کرے اسی طرح ہفتے کے روز چاررکعت نماز پڑھ کر حضرت امیر المومنین علی ابن ابی طالب ؑ کو ہدیہ کرے۔ نیز ہر روز چار رکعت نماز پڑھے،اور ترتیب کے ساتھ ایک ایک امامؑ کوہدیہ کرتا رہے یہاں تک کہ جمعرات کے دن نماز پڑھ کر حضرت امام جعفر صادق ؑ کے لئے ہدیہ کرے پھر روزِ جمعہ آٹھ رکعت نماز ادا کرے اور پہلے کی طرح رسول خدا ؐ اور حضرت فاطمۃ الزہرا ؑکو ہدیہ پیش کرے۔اگلے روز یعنی ہفتہ کے دن چاررکعت نماز پڑھ کر حضرت امام موسیٰ کاظم ؑ کو ہدیہ پیش کرے اور اسی طرح روزانہ چار ررکعت نماز پڑھ کر ترتیب کے ساتھ ہر امام کو ہدیہ کرتا جائے چنانچہ جمعرات کے دن چار رکعت نماز بجا لاکر حضرت امام العصرؑ عجل اللہ فرجہ،کے لئے ہدیہ کرے اور ہر دوسری رکعت کے بعد یہ دعا پڑھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSi